      "name": "Blog App",
      "summary": "The BlogApp export defines a comprehensive blog management system that includes functionality for creating, editing, and organizing blog posts, author bios, and categories. It provides a user interface for content administration, including admin views with metadata editing, filtering, sorting, and publishing controls. The application supports multiple presentation modes, such as site view with a magazine layout and admin view with detailed post controls. Additionally, it enables drag-and-drop organization of featured posts, lead stories, and associated media, along with site-wide theme customization. Its primary purpose is to facilitate both content creation and presentation for a blog or news site with flexible theming, content management, and display formats.",
